{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/2/context.json","@id":"https://iiif.bodleian.ox.ac.uk/iiif/manifest/fd529c18-c227-457b-8c53-2fce5e882807.json","@type":"sc:Manifest","label":"Bodleian Library MS.Chin.c.18","description":"清代外銷畫花卉昆蟲十二幅 冊","metadata":[{"label":"Homepage","value":"<span><a href=\"https://digital.bodleian.ox.ac.uk/objects/fd529c18-c227-457b-8c53-2fce5e882807/\">View on Digital Bodleian</a></span>"},{"label":"Title","value":"清代外銷畫花卉昆蟲十二幅 冊"},{"label":"Other Titles","value":"An album of twelve Chinese export paintings of flowers and insects"},{"label":"Other Titles","value":"Twelve paintings of flowers and insects by a Cantonese"},{"label":"Shelfmark","value":"Bodleian Library MS.Chin.c.18"},{"label":"Author","value":"Chowkwa"},{"label":"Language","value":"No linguistic content"},{"label":"Date Statement","value":"清代"},{"label":"Place of Origin","value":"China, Canton [Guangzhou]"},{"label":"Description","value":"An album comprising 12 Chinese export paintings of flowers and insects. The paintings were created by Chowkwa, Painter and Copier of Charts, in Canton [Guangzhou] during the Qing dynasty."},{"label":"Contents Note","value":"Chinese export paintings are usually produced in large quantity, therefore, there may be other existing copies. 外銷畫，多為批量生產，可能多有存世。"},{"label":"Contents Note","value":"Inside upper cover: S.C.33023."},{"label":"Contents Note","value":"Inside upper cover: Unrecognized scripts could be Bengali."},{"label":"Contents Note","value":"Inside lower cover: Chowkwa, Painter and Copier of Charts"},{"label":"Contents Note","value":"Theme: portrait."},{"label":"Materials","value":"Pith paper"},{"label":"Hand","value":"Watercolour. 水彩畫。"},{"label":"Extent","value":"Fourteen folios, including twelve paintings. 一冊共十四開，本幅十二幅，前副頁和后副頁各一開一幅。"},{"label":"Decoration","value":"This album contains twelve paintings."},{"label":"Binding","value":"The cover and back cover are mounted with yellow silk fabric featuring red, pink, blue, and green patterns. The painting core is framed with green striped silk fabric on white paper. The cover and back cover are encased in a book cover made of black waterproof fabric. 冊。畫冊，内含十二幅畫。封面和封底由黃色帶有紅、粉、藍、綠四色花紋的絲織物裝裱， 畫心由綠色條狀絲織物為框裝裱在白色紙本上。封面和封底上包有用黑色防水織物製作的書皮。"},{"label":"Provenance","value":"On the inside of upper cover, a seal in red colour is found, showing Chowkwa Painter and Copier of Charts, indicating the painter. Previous shelfmark: S.C.33023 (as indicated on the inside upper board). Acquired in 1901."},{"label":"Record Origin","value":"Description based on a catalogue record prepared by Boya Zhang, 2024."},{"label":"Collection","value":"Chinese Maps, Manuscripts and Printed Books"},{"label":"Record Created","value":"2024-06-07T13:05:31Z"},{"label":"Holding Institution","value":"Bodleian Libraries, University of Oxford"},{"label":"Digitization Sponsor","value":"<span>鍾瀚德基金會 (Chung Hon-Dak Fund)</span>"}],"navDate":"1700-01-01T00:00:00Z","rendering":{"@id":"https://digital.bodleian.ox.ac.uk/objects/fd529c18-c227-457b-8c53-2fce5e882807/","label":"View on Digital Bodleian","format":"text/html"},"attribution":"<span>Photo: © Bodleian Libraries, University of Oxford. Terms of use: <a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/\">CC BY-NC 4.0</a>. For more information, please see <a href=\"https://digital.bodleian.ox.ac.uk/terms/\">https://digital.bodleian.ox.ac.uk/terms/</a></span>","logo":{"@id":"https://iiif.bodleian.ox.ac.uk/iiif/image/f27e28db-0b08-4f16-9bdf-3565f591fb71/full/256,/0/default.jpg","@type":"dctypes:Image","format":"image/jpeg","service":{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/image/2/context.json","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/2/level1.json","@id":"https://iiif.bodleian.ox.ac.uk/iiif/image/f27e28db-0b08-4f16-9bdf-3565f591fb71"}},"thumbnail":{"@id":"https://iiif.bodleian.ox.ac.uk/iiif/image/a8864939-9d6a-4490-a0ba-b134895bed55/full/256,/0/default.jpg","@type":"dctypes:Image","format":"image/jpeg","service":{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/imag